QuickCHM
========

Installation
============
 1. Copy quickchm.qlgenerator to /System/Library/QuickLook
 2. Relaunch finder 

ChangeLog
=========

1.2 
    * 64 bits
    * Mac OS X 10.8

1.1		
    * Universal binary build
    * Preview is now generated as HTML
    * Thumbnails are generated in the same thread as plugin main thread, eliminated thread issue and potential memory leak
    * Performance enhancement
    * Experimental multi-page preview(only works in command-line preview)

1.0
    * Generate preview as image
    * Generate thumbnail using URL loading protocols